{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":false,"promptId":"1ff7d7cf-2ef9-4551-9b82-d4a55c50d994","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"Help me reconfigure as per advice below.  Do you understand this?\n\n\nExpected behavior — you're still on the `stable` channel, so the background auto-updater pulled you back to the stable version (2.1.98). `claude install <version>` doesn't change the channel or set a floor.\n\nTwo fixes:\n\n**Switch to the `latest` channel (recommended if you want 2.1.114+):**\n```\nclaude\n/config\n```\nSet auto-update channel → `latest`. Exit and restart.\n\n**Or stay on `stable` but pin a floor** — edit `~/.claude/settings.json`:\n```json\n{\n  \"autoUpdatesChannel\": \"stable\",\n  \"minimumVersion\": \"2.1.114\"\n}\n```\nThe auto-updater refuses to install anything below `minimumVersion`, so you'll hold at 2.1.114 until stable catches up.\n\nThen `claude install 2.1.114` again and it should stick."},"uuid":"45d5c5ee-11a6-463b-b625-95c1280905b6","timestamp":"2026-04-18T15:59:17.925Z","permissionMode":"default","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/bhyslop/projects/rbm_alpha_recipemuster","sessionId":"4fdf0f9c-8762-4b78-99e8-bd6e07204b5d","version":"2.1.98","gitBranch":"main"}
